<p>Bonuses: You can get bonus when you win a multi bet with no less than 5 selections. Bonuses start from 5% of the Potential Winning (for 5 selections) and it increases by 5% for each extra selection added to the betslip, to up to 130%.</p>
<p>Bonuses are applied to all selections with odds above 1.20. Bonuses are an extra winning that we offer you at SportyBet, and bonuses can be used to substitute real money when placing bets or withdrawing.</p>
<p>Bonuses are permanently valid in your account.</p>
