<p>Gifts: these are different from Bonuses. Gifts cannot be withdrawn from your account.</p>
<p>SportyBet offers two types of Gifts:</p>
<ol>
<li><p>Cash Gifts, these are reduced from the value of the Total Stake, and do not have any constraints when placing a Bet.</p>
</li>
<li><p>Coupon Gifts, these offer a discount when spending a required amount of money when placing a Bet. It is of conditional use.</p>
</li>
</ol>
<p>All Gifts have an expiry date. Please, go to &quot;My Account&quot; to check all obtained Gifts by clicking on &quot;Gifts&quot;.</p>
<p>If you are interested in the latest promotions, please go to the &quot;Promotions&quot; page to view more ongoing campaigns.</p>
